snippet.title: Mendel Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Mendel is a game about using genetics to create surreal, beautiful gardens on the far off planet of Kepler-186F.

For more information, check out the game's blog: http://mendelgame.tumblr.com

The music used in the trailer is by Chris Zabriske: http://chriszabriskie.com
